fs.fibu2.view.render
Class EntryDialogFactory

java.lang.Object
  fs.fibu2.data.event.JournalAdapter
      fs.fibu2.view.render.EntryDialogFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
JournalListener, ReadingPointListener, java.util.EventListener
public final class EntryDialogFactory
extends JournalAdapter

This class creates EntryDialogs. It takes care that for each entry in a given journal there is at most one dialog and that a dialog is disposed when its associated entry is deleted.

Author:
Simon Hampe
